을 알리가 없지.............나두 그 맘때는 나물류는 쳐다도 안 봤는데~~ㅋㅋ             날이 많이 춥네요.....첫째군은 오늘 쉰다고 룰루랄라 둘째군과 진영양은 학교에 가야 하는 설움이~ㅋㅋ   이제 시험이 시작 되었겠죠.   모든 수험생들 홧~ 팅~~!! 입니다~^^            ","images":["http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141113_154/pingu528_14158052767886Ubev_JPEG/IMG_7438.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141113_188/pingu528_14158052775214AmsW_JPEG/IMG_7458.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141113_232/pingu528_1415805278019NgprK_JPEG/IMG_7411.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141113_125/pingu528_1415805279581Xjvov_JPEG/IMG_7419.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141113_270/pingu528_1415805279967LNVBj_JPEG/IMG_7421.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141113_29/pingu528_1415805280343Imda2_JPEG/IMG_7423.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141113_6/pingu528_1415805278587FdK7P_JPEG/IMG_7416.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141113_202/pingu528_1415805280754HLr3i_JPEG/IMG_7426.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141113_44/pingu528_1415805279097zJNY7_JPEG/IMG_7417.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141113_180/pingu528_1415805281174i5Irn_JPEG/IMG_7428.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141113_222/pingu528_1415805281918q9IPN_JPEG/IMG_7444.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141113_300/pingu528_1415805282690cinAu_JPEG/IMG_7445.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141113_213/pingu528_1415805283061ho5bB_JPEG/IMG_7447.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141113_180/pingu528_1415805283552wf5H5_JPEG/IMG_7452.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141113_283/pingu528_1415805284162j4Imh_JPEG/IMG_7455.JPG?type="],"nickname":"웅이맘","id":"웅이맘","comment_no":0,"like":0}
